name: Oversummoned, Overpowered, and Over It!
author: Saitousa
content: High school student Takafuji Inori, along with his classmates, gets summoned to another world. Just as he was expecting to begin a new life, a magic circle suddenly appears beneath him again, and he is recklessly summoned to yet another world! After repeated summonings, what remains in Inoriâ€™s possession are numerous protagonist-level, overpowered abilities...
